Find the year anchor. Starting with year [34mY[39m:
 - note the century anchor [3mA[23m
 - take the last two digits [3mT = [3mY % 100[23m[23m
 - the resulting increment is [3mI = [3mT + T/4[23m[23m
 - add the century anchor to get [3mW = [3m[33mA + I[39m[23m[23m

